## StreamEventHandlers.onComplete() method

Called when the stream completes without errors.

**Signature:**

```typescript
onComplete?(): void;
```
**Returns:**

void

## Remarks

Completion indicates the underlying transport ended naturally (e.g. the server closed the connection after sending all data).
